
IBM Bluemix tools used:
Twitter Insights
AlchemyAPI
DashDB


For trial and presentation purpose the test company consider is: Reliance Comunication

Raw Data Collected using web crawller and Twitter Insights. 

The news articles collected by the crawler is used to perform the sentiment analysis using AlchemyAPI.

The whole model was then uploaded to dash dp for cleaning and filling empty values.

The training data takes information of 3 month period in time axis. Linear correlation between News artical sentiments for a given date, 
Twitter sentiments for a lag of 4-7 days after publication of article and NSE data for the given time is established. 

The prediction modal then make use of the whole data frame to predtict the future movement in stock market.

